        "created_at": "2022-08-17T11:12:15.906Z",
        "cooked": "<p>A few very advanced, low-yielding parcels are getting picked this weekend, but you can expect things to get underway around the middle of next week in the Beaujolais, and towards the end of next week and over the weekend for whites in the C\u00f4te d\u2019Or.</p>",
